{"id":259469,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/快乐放飞-快速移民/","date":"2012-10-27T07:05:47Z","modified":"2012-10-27T07:05:47Z","title":"快乐放飞 快速移民","content":"<p>@连鹏：今日《宁波晚报》头版刊出大幅移民广告，头条：快乐放飞。这是无声的抗议么？这种高级讽刺的背后也让人觉得悲哀，当媒体无法自由报道，民众无法对身边发生的关乎切身利益的事畅所欲言，除了逃离，还能怎样？</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/%e5%bf%ab%e4%b9%90%e6%94%be%e9%a3%9e-%e5%bf%ab%e9%80%9f%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91/61d634bajw1dy9r8g5zhyj/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-259470\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-259470\" title=\"\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/61d634bajw1dy9r8g5zhyj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"350\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/61d634bajw1dy9r8g5zhyj.jpg 350w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/61d634bajw1dy9r8g5zhyj-220x300.jpg 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18269,13789],"tags":[20744,20743]}